if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb740c4a0a1781eaece7193a8f02030321d96f7","tid":2262682,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:58:17.000Z","msg":"據案情指，當天晚上7時許，有近50至100名示威者在大埔超級城外集結，其間有人衝擊警方防線並向警方投擲磚塊石頭等硬物。警方發射催淚彈，有男子踩電動滑板向警方投汽油彈，汽油彈隨後爆炸。至8時許，警方向人群發出警告，有示威者不予理會，向警方發射雷射光束。警方向示威者推進並拘捕案中四人，從梁姓被告身上搜出士巴拿和防毒面具等物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/ER7PTGPE7BBWVJAHKUWN2554P4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FER7PTGPE7BBWVJAHKUWN2554P4%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=7948601d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FER7PTGPE7BBWVJAHKUWN2554P4%2F&h=53275e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/ER7PTGPE7BBWVJAHKUWN2554P4/</a>"}]}